Source: globus-repository
Section: net
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Globus Support <support@globus.org>
Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 7), autotools-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.3
Homepage: http://www.globus.org/

Package: globus-repository-@RELEASENAME@
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Globus Binary Repository Package
 This package contains the sources.list(5) file to access the official
 Globus Toolkit repository, as well as tasksel(8) definitions for package
 groups for the Globus Toolkit.

